<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Benediction" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Benediction,</orth> blessing: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.614" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 614</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.156" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 156</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.3.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 3, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.58" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.350" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 350</bibl>. <cit><quote>thou out of heaven's b. comest to the warm sun,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.2.168" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 2, 168</bibl></cit> (modification of the proverb: <emph>out of God's blessing into the warm sun).</emph>
